<view class="page wallet-index-page"><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="notice-bar warning" bindtap="{{d}}"><image class="notice-icon-img" src="{{b}}" mode="aspectFit"/><text class="notice-text">保证金低于最低要求，线路已对车商隐藏</text><text class="notice-action">去充值</text><image class="arrow-icon" src="{{c}}" mode="aspectFit"/></view><view wx:if="{{e}}" class="notice-bar danger" bindtap="{{h}}"><image class="notice-icon-img" src="{{f}}" mode="aspectFit"/><text class="notice-text">信息服务费已耗尽，无法确认接单或联系客户</text><text class="notice-action">去充值</text><image class="arrow-icon" src="{{g}}" mode="aspectFit"/></view><view class="section balance-card deposit"><view class="row-between align-center"><view class="balance-meta"><text class="balance-label">货运保证金 (元)</text><text class="balance-value font-bold">{{i}}</text></view><button class="primary-btn recharge-btn-mini" bindtap="{{j}}">充值</button></view><view class="balance-footer"><text>最低限额标准: {{k}}</text><text class="{{['status-tag', 'mini-tag', m]}}">{{l}}</text></view></view><view class="section balance-card info-fee"><view class="row-between align-center"><view class="balance-meta"><text class="balance-label">信息服务费 (元)</text><text class="balance-value font-bold">{{n}}</text></view><button class="primary-btn recharge-btn-mini" bindtap="{{o}}">充值</button></view><view class="balance-footer"><text>按单按次确认扣费, 多充不限</text><text class="{{['status-tag', 'mini-tag', q]}}">{{p}}</text></view></view><view class="section links-section-card"><view class="section-title">资金与消费记录</view><view class="links-list"><view class="link-item" bindtap="{{t}}"><view class="row align-center"><image class="link-icon" src="{{r}}" mode="aspectFit"/><text class="link-label">在线充值记录</text></view><image class="link-arrow" src="{{s}}" mode="aspectFit"/></view><view class="link-item" bindtap="{{x}}"><view class="row align-center"><image class="link-icon" src="{{v}}" mode="aspectFit"/><text class="link-label">订单信息费扣费清单</text></view><image class="link-arrow" src="{{w}}" mode="aspectFit"/></view><view class="link-item" bindtap="{{A}}"><view class="row align-center"><image class="link-icon" src="{{y}}" mode="aspectFit"/><text class="link-label">钱包变更账单总流水</text></view><image class="link-arrow" src="{{z}}" mode="aspectFit"/></view></view></view></view>